<pb n="0785c" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0514.0785c"/>
<lb n="0785c01" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0785c02" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 514 [Nos. 515, 516]</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0785c03" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead>佛說諫王<note n="0785018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（一卷）【聖】</note><app n="0785018"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">經一卷</rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0785c04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0785c05" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0785019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">宋安陽侯＝宋居士【宋】【宮】，劉宋居士【元】【明】，〔宋安…譯〕－【聖】</note><note n="0785019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔宋安陽侯沮渠京聲譯〕－【聖】，宋安陽侯＝宋居士【宋】【宮】，宋安陽侯＝劉宋居士【元】【明】</note><app n="0785019"><lem wit="【大】">宋安陽侯沮渠京聲譯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">宋居士沮渠京聲譯</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">劉宋居士沮渠京聲譯</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0785c06" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT14p0785c0601"><note n="0785020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如是我聞＝聞如是【三】【宮】</note><note n="0785020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如是我聞＝聞如是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0785020"><lem wit="【大】">如是我聞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">聞如是</rdg></app>：</p><p xml:id="pT14p0785c0605" rend="inline">一時，佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。
<lb n="0785c07" ed="T"/><note n="0785021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔是時國〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0785021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔是時國〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0785021"><lem wit="【大】">是時，國</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>王名不離先尼，出行國界，道過佛所，
<lb n="0785c08" ed="T"/>身蒙塵土，解劍退<note n="0785022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蓋＝坐【聖】</note><app n="0785022"><lem wit="【大】">蓋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">坐</rdg></app>為佛作禮。<note n="0785023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天＝世【明】</note><app n="0785023"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">世</rdg></app>尊曰：「就
<lb n="0785c09" ed="T"/>坐。」王即坐。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0785c0905" rend="inline">佛問王：「王所從來，身蒙塵土。」王即
<lb n="0785c10" ed="T"/>退坐，稽首對：「諾！屬行國界有災異者。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0785c1015" rend="inline">佛告王
<lb n="0785c11" ed="T"/><note n="0785024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔曰〕－【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0785024"><lem wit="【大】">曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>：「王治當以<note n="0785025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">正＝政【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0785025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">正＝政【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0785025"><lem wit="【大】">正</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">政</rdg></app>法，無失節度，常以慈心養
<lb n="0785c12" ed="T"/>育人民，所以得霸治。為<note n="0785026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔國〕－【聖】</note><app n="0785026"><lem wit="【大】">國</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>王者，皆由宿命
<lb n="0785c13" ed="T"/>行善所致，統理民事不可偏枉。諸公卿群<note n="0785027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">寮＝僚【聖】＊</note><app n="0785027"><lem wit="【大】">寮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">僚</rdg></app>
<lb n="0785c14" ed="T"/>下逮凡民皆有怨辭，<note n="0785028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔王治〕－【三】【宮】，〔王〕－【聖】</note><note n="0785028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔王治〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，〔王〕－【聖】</note><app n="0785028"><lem wit="【大】">王治</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">治</rdg></app><note n="0785029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">行＝正【聖】</note><app n="0785029"><lem wit="【大】">行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">正</rdg></app>不<note n="0785030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">平＋（等）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0785030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">平＋（等）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0785030"><lem wit="【大】">平</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">平等</rdg></app>海內皆
<lb n="0785c15" ed="T"/>忿，身死<note n="0785031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔魂〕－【聖】</note><app n="0785031"><lem wit="【大】">魂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>神<note n="0785032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">常＝當【三】【宮】，〔常〕－【聖】</note><note n="0785032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">常＝當【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，〔常〕－【聖】</note><app n="0785032"><lem wit="【大】">常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">當</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>入太山地獄，後雖悔之無
<lb n="0785c16" ed="T"/>所復及。王治國平<app type="star" corresp="#0785025"><lem wit="【大】">正</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">政</rdg></app>常以節度，臣民歎德
<lb n="0785c17" ed="T"/>四海歸心，天、龍、鬼神皆聞王善，死得上天後
<lb n="0785c18" ed="T"/>亦無悔。王無好<note n="0785033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婬妷＝婬泆【元】，淫泆【明】</note><note n="0785033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婬妷＝婬泆【元】，＝淫泆【明】</note><app n="0785033"><lem wit="【大】">婬妷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">婬泆</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">淫泆</rdg></app>以自荒<note n="0785034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">壞＝懷【聖】</note><app n="0785034"><lem wit="【大】">壞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">懷</rdg></app>，無以忿意
<lb n="0785c19" ed="T"/>有所殘賊，當受忠臣剛直之諫，夫與人言，常
<lb n="0785c20" ed="T"/>以寬詳無灼熱之。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0785c2008" rend="inline">「當以四意待於國民。何謂
<lb n="0785c21" ed="T"/>為四？隨時廩與，和意與語，所有珍寶與民
<lb n="0785c22" ed="T"/>共之，<note n="0785035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">占＝瞻【聖】</note><app n="0785035"><lem wit="【大】">占</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">瞻</rdg></app>視老病及諸<note n="0785036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鰥＝孤【聖】</note><app n="0785036"><lem wit="【大】">鰥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">孤</rdg></app>寡。王如是者，國中
<lb n="0785c23" ed="T"/>和平即得其福，壽終上天所願自然。王不可
<lb n="0785c24" ed="T"/>以常得自在，人皆敬畏以之為樂，名象、好馬、
<lb n="0785c25" ed="T"/>寶車、賢臣，群<app type="star" corresp="#0785027"><lem wit="【大】">寮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">僚</rdg></app>百官導從前後，內藏珍寶
<lb n="0785c26" ed="T"/>倉<note n="0785037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">庫＝穀【聖】</note><app n="0785037"><lem wit="【大】">庫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">穀</rdg></app>百物，皆當腐壞無長存者。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0785c2613" rend="inline">「年少會老
<lb n="0785c27" ed="T"/>強健必病，含血之類皆當歸死，珍寶、妻子、<note n="0785038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">家室＝室家【聖】</note><app n="0785038"><lem wit="【大】">家
<lb n="0785c28" ed="T"/>室</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">室家</rdg></app>內外不可<note n="0785039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">常得＝得常【聖】</note><app n="0785039"><lem wit="【大】">常得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">得常</rdg></app>，如人夢見殿舍、好園、樹木、
<lb n="0785c29" ed="T"/><note n="0785040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">花果＝生菓【宋】【元】【宮】，生果【明】，生葉【聖】</note><note n="0785040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">花果＝生菓【宋】【元】【宮】，＝生果【明】，＝生葉【聖】</note><app n="0785040"><lem wit="【大】">花果</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">生菓</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">生果</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">生葉</rdg></app>、池水、流泉，遊戲其中快樂無極，寤則
<pb n="0786a" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0514.0786a"/>
<lb n="0786a01" ed="T"/>霍然莫知所在，覩世所有皆如人夢。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0786a0115" rend="inline">「王寧見
<lb n="0786a02" ed="T"/>樹有華果，華果不能常著樹，青青之葉會有
<lb n="0786a03" ed="T"/>萎落；天冠、巾幘、黼<note n="0786001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">黻＝<unclear/>【聖】</note><app n="0786001"><lem wit="【大】">黻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><unclear/></rdg></app>、名服不能常好，流水不
<lb n="0786a04" ed="T"/>能常滿；放火曠野，火盛焰赫不久則滅；暴風、
<lb n="0786a05" ed="T"/>疾雨、雷電霹靂，斯<note n="0786002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">臾＝須【聖】</note><app n="0786002"><lem wit="【大】">臾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">須</rdg></app>之間霍然不<note n="0786003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見＝現【聖】</note><app n="0786003"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">現</rdg></app>，日欲
<lb n="0786a06" ed="T"/>出時星無精光，日之盛明照於天下不久<note n="0786004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">則＝復【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0786004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">則＝復【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786004"><lem wit="【大】">則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">復</rdg></app>
<lb n="0786a07" ed="T"/>冥，世間無常亦復如是。喻如四面有大石山，
<lb n="0786a08" ed="T"/>上下皆有六山俱<note n="0786005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">到＝至【聖】</note><app n="0786005"><lem wit="【大】">到</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">至</rdg></app>同時共合，其中人物含
<lb n="0786a09" ed="T"/>血之類，無有豪賤皆當<note n="0786006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">糜＝磨【聖】</note><app n="0786006"><lem wit="【大】">糜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">磨</rdg></app>碎。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0786a0912" rend="inline">「人有四事不
<lb n="0786a10" ed="T"/>可得止：老至體枯、病來心惱、身死神去、所
<lb n="0786a11" ed="T"/>有珍寶皆當棄捐不可得保，此四一至不可
<lb n="0786a12" ed="T"/>得離無避逃處，非口所能守請陳謝，不可<note n="0786007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">財＝以餞【聖】</note><app n="0786007"><lem wit="【大】">財</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">以餞</rdg></app>
<lb n="0786a13" ed="T"/>許求哀得解。是時，所有名象、良馬、珍寶、壯士、
<lb n="0786a14" ed="T"/>群臣、百官護導前後，孰能為王排却之者？王
<lb n="0786a15" ed="T"/>寧見師子，獸中最猛，遙見群鹿意欲所取，便
<lb n="0786a16" ed="T"/>前搏撮裂食其肉，如斯之痛安可言乎？<note n="0786008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">命＝喻【聖】</note><app n="0786008"><lem wit="【大】">命</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">喻</rdg></app>如
<lb n="0786a17" ed="T"/>師子取群鹿時，人命欲終身體不寧，血脈為
<lb n="0786a18" ed="T"/>消面色為變，命日欲促，五<note n="0786009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">藏＝臟【三】【宮】</note><note n="0786009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">藏＝臟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0786009"><lem wit="【大】">藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">臟</rdg></app>不治不思飲食，
<lb n="0786a19" ed="T"/>雖有神呪、良醫、善藥不能使愈。口為妄語，其
<lb n="0786a20" ed="T"/>所索者家室恣之，身體皆痛如被掠治，手足
<lb n="0786a21" ed="T"/><note n="0786010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">抂＝狂【宋】【宮】，恇【元】【明】</note><note n="0786010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">抂＝狂【宋】【宮】，＝恇【元】【明】</note><app n="0786010"><lem wit="【大】">抂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">狂</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">恇</rdg></app>攘骨節欲解，口乾息極羸瘦困劣，不能起
<lb n="0786a22" ed="T"/>居坐臥須人；若得良藥糜粥甘食人當含之，
<lb n="0786a23" ed="T"/><note n="0786011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">必＝心【聖】</note><app n="0786011"><lem wit="【大】">必</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">心</rdg></app>復苦極筋脈欲<note n="0786012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">絕＝斷【聖】</note><app n="0786012"><lem wit="【大】">絕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">斷</rdg></app>，但有出氣無復報入，
<lb n="0786a24" ed="T"/>脣燥乾焦，正氣竭盡邪氣在處；舌稍却縮面
<lb n="0786a25" ed="T"/>目無色，耳鼻閉塞不聞聲香，手足拘攣筋急，
<lb n="0786a26" ed="T"/>口噤欲言不能，手或把空<note n="0786013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">莫索＝摸𢱢【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0786013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">莫索＝摸𢱢【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786013"><lem wit="【大】">莫索</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">摸𢱢</rdg></app>邊傍，<note n="0786014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">白＝自【元】，身【明】</note><note n="0786014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">白＝自【元】，＝身【明】</note><app n="0786014"><lem wit="【大】">白</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">自</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">身</rdg></app>汗
<lb n="0786a27" ed="T"/>目淚流出相<note n="0786015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">續＝屬【聖】</note><app n="0786015"><lem wit="【大】">續</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">屬</rdg></app>，心意著痛識轉消滅無所復
<lb n="0786a28" ed="T"/>知，<note n="0786016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">熅＝溫【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0786016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">熅＝溫【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786016"><lem wit="【大】">熅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">溫</rdg></app>去身冷魂神去矣。所有珍寶、父母、兄弟、
<lb n="0786a29" ed="T"/>妻子，內外知識、奴婢皆當棄捐，隨行獨去不
<pb n="0786b" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0514.0786b"/>
<lb n="0786b01" ed="T"/><note n="0786017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">知所到＝得自在【聖】</note><app n="0786017"><lem wit="【大】">知所到</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">得自在</rdg></app>，世間雖樂不得久留。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0786b0112" rend="inline">「王當是時當何
<lb n="0786b02" ed="T"/>恃怙？唯有孝<note n="0786018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">順慈養＝慈育養【聖】</note><app n="0786018"><lem wit="【大】">順慈養</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">慈育養</rdg></app>二親，供事高行清潔沙
<lb n="0786b03" ed="T"/>門，<note n="0786019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見凡＝凡見【聖】</note><app n="0786019"><lem wit="【大】">見凡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">凡見</rdg></app>老人當尊敬之，所有財寶與民同
<lb n="0786b04" ed="T"/>歡，當以<note n="0786020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慈＝善【聖】</note><app n="0786020"><lem wit="【大】">慈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">善</rdg></app>心施惠於民，無以讒言殘<note n="0786021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">害民＝賊人【聖】</note><app n="0786021"><lem wit="【大】">害民</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">賊人</rdg></app>
<lb n="0786b05" ed="T"/>命，為王之法當宣聖道，教民為善，<note n="0786022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【聖】</note><app n="0786022"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">惟</rdg></app>守一
<lb n="0786b06" ed="T"/>心，心存三尊。王者如斯，諸聖諮嗟，天、龍、鬼神
<lb n="0786b07" ed="T"/>擁護其國，生有榮譽死得上天。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0786b0713" rend="inline">「身死神去，當
<lb n="0786b08" ed="T"/>何所恃？<note n="0786023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惟＝唯【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0786023"><lem wit="【大】">惟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】【聖】">唯</rdg></app>恃善耳。火盛煒<note n="0786024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">煒＝燁【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0786024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">煒＝燁【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786024"><lem wit="【大】">煒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">燁</rdg></app>恃水滅之，飢
<lb n="0786b09" ed="T"/>渴之人<note n="0786025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惟＝唯【三】【宮】</note><note n="0786025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惟＝唯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0786025"><lem wit="【大】">惟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">唯</rdg></app>恃水穀，老恃机杖，盲恃有目，冥
<lb n="0786b10" ed="T"/>恃燈火，疾病困篤恃良醫藥，船行巨海風浪
<lb n="0786b11" ed="T"/><note n="0786026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盛猛＝猛盛【聖】</note><app n="0786026"><lem wit="【大】">盛猛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">猛盛</rdg></app>恃彼<note n="0786027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">榜櫓＝傍岸【聖】</note><app n="0786027"><lem wit="【大】">榜櫓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">傍岸</rdg></app>，道有<note n="0786028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盜賊＝賊盜【聖】</note><app n="0786028"><lem wit="【大】">盜賊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">賊盜</rdg></app>恃藏匿處。身死
<lb n="0786b12" ed="T"/>神去<note n="0786029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惟＝唯【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0786029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惟＝唯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786029"><lem wit="【大】">惟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">唯</rdg></app><note n="0786030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">恃修＝脩恃【聖】</note><app n="0786030"><lem wit="【大】">恃修</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">脩恃</rdg></app>善，<note n="0786031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">猶＝由【聖】</note><app n="0786031"><lem wit="【大】">猶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">由</rdg></app>逢彼難各恃其事，以
<lb n="0786b13" ed="T"/>自拔濟宗室獲安。王無以為樂飲食極味，遊
<lb n="0786b14" ed="T"/>居自在<note n="0786032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔不可〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0786032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔不可〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0786032"><lem wit="【大】">不可</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>常<note n="0786033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">得＝恃【聖】</note><app n="0786033"><lem wit="【大】">得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">恃</rdg></app>，飽滿皆當消散不可常
<lb n="0786b15" ed="T"/>得，好香塗身苾芬<note n="0786034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">括＝聒【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0786034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">括＝聒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786034"><lem wit="【大】">括</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">聒</rdg></app>鼻，珠璣瓔珞奕奕<note n="0786035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曜＝耀【聖】</note><app n="0786035"><lem wit="【大】">曜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">耀</rdg></app>
<lb n="0786b16" ed="T"/>目，水陸好華<note n="0786036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以為＝為以【聖】</note><app n="0786036"><lem wit="【大】">以為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">為以</rdg></app><note n="0786037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">校＝博【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786037"><lem wit="【大】">校</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】【聖】">博</rdg></app>飾，金縷織成以為名
<lb n="0786b17" ed="T"/>服：白毳衣、文繡衣、雜綵衣、無極衣、細疊衣、
<lb n="0786b18" ed="T"/>細緻衣、<note n="0786038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">錦＝繡【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786038"><lem wit="【大】">錦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】【聖】">繡</rdg></app>綾衣，此皆無常不可久保。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0786b1815" rend="inline">「宮觀
<lb n="0786b19" ed="T"/>高臺華闕殿舍，黃金、白銀、七寶床㯓，氍<note n="0786039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">毹＝氀【聖】</note><app n="0786039"><lem wit="【大】">毹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">氀</rdg></app>𣰅
<lb n="0786b20" ed="T"/>㲪綩綖細軟以藉身體，<note n="0786040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">七寶＝金縷【聖】</note><app n="0786040"><lem wit="【大】">七寶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">金縷</rdg></app>織成文繡綾綺
<lb n="0786b21" ed="T"/>以為幃帳，柱梁<note n="0786041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">殿＝壁【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0786041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">殿＝壁【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786041"><lem wit="【大】">殿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">壁</rdg></app>戶彫文刻鏤，燒眾雜香遊
<lb n="0786b22" ed="T"/>戲其中，斯皆無常不可久保。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0786b2212" rend="inline">「琴瑟、箏笛眾<note n="0786042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">音＝樂【聖】</note><app n="0786042"><lem wit="【大】">音</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">樂</rdg></app>
<lb n="0786b23" ed="T"/>集聚，歌舞倡伎眾音盈耳快樂<note n="0786043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（不）＋可【聖】</note><app n="0786043"><lem wit="【大】">可</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">不可</rdg></app>言，斯亦無
<lb n="0786b24" ed="T"/>常，如<note n="0786044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">幻如夢＝夢幻【聖】</note><app n="0786044"><lem wit="【大】">幻如夢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">夢幻</rdg></app>不<note n="0786045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">得＝可【聖】</note><app n="0786045"><lem wit="【大】">得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">可</rdg></app>久保。象馬寶車光目之
<lb n="0786b25" ed="T"/>觀，王一出時<note n="0786046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">椎＝推【聖】＊</note><app n="0786046"><lem wit="【大】">椎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">推</rdg></app>鐘鳴鼓<note n="0786047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">驛＝護【聖】</note><app n="0786047"><lem wit="【大】">驛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">護</rdg></app>導前後，王乘羽
<lb n="0786b26" ed="T"/>蓋之車侍者持幢，翠毛<note n="0786048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">䳰＝葆【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0786048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">䳰＝葆【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786048"><lem wit="【大】">䳰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">葆</rdg></app>羽彫文其柄以拂
<lb n="0786b27" ed="T"/>塵土，治填道路丹畫欄楯，眾民所觀無不敬
<lb n="0786b28" ed="T"/>畏，好華名香皆以迎王，稱壽萬歲斯亦難保。</p>
<lb n="0786b29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT14p0786b2901">「王寧見人欲死<note n="0786049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時不＝之時【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0786049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">時不＝之時【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786049"><lem wit="【大】">時不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">之時</rdg></app>？諸家內外聚會其邊，
<pb n="0786c" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0514.0786c"/>
<lb n="0786c01" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0786046"><lem wit="【大】">椎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">推</rdg></app>胸呼天皆云奈何，<note n="0786050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">喐＝哊【聖】</note><app n="0786050"><lem wit="【大】">喐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">哊</rdg></app><note n="0786051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吚＝咿【三】【宮】</note><note n="0786051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吚＝咿【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0786051"><lem wit="【大】">吚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">咿</rdg></app>哽<note n="0786052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">咽＝噎【聖】</note><app n="0786052"><lem wit="【大】">咽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">噎</rdg></app>淚下交
<lb n="0786c02" ed="T"/><note n="0786053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">流＝橫【聖】</note><app n="0786053"><lem wit="【大】">流</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">橫</rdg></app>，嗚呼痛哉神靈獨逝：『<note n="0786054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔捨〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0786054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔捨〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0786054"><lem wit="【大】">捨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>吾如之<note n="0786055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔乎〕－【聖】</note><app n="0786055"><lem wit="【大】">乎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>！』聞
<lb n="0786c03" ed="T"/>之者莫不傷心，<note n="0786056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">覩＝視【聖】</note><app n="0786056"><lem wit="【大】">覩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">視</rdg></app>之者莫不助哀。載之出城
<lb n="0786c04" ed="T"/>捐於曠野，飛鳥走獸<note n="0786057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摑<g ref="#CB02622"/>＝𤡓<g ref="#CB02622"/>【三】【宮】，掣抴【聖】</note><note n="0786057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">摑<g ref="#CB02622"/>＝𤡓<g ref="#CB02622"/>【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，＝掣抴【聖】</note><app n="0786057"><lem wit="【大】">摑<g ref="#CB02622"/></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">𤡓<g ref="#CB02622"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">掣抴</rdg></app>食之，身中有蟲
<lb n="0786c05" ed="T"/>還食其肉，日炙風飄骨皆為乾，往昔諸王尊
<lb n="0786c06" ed="T"/>榮豪貴，隱隱闐闐亦如大王，今日霍然不復
<lb n="0786c07" ed="T"/>見之。此<note n="0786058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">皆＝者【聖】</note><app n="0786058"><lem wit="【大】">皆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">者</rdg></app>無常之明<note n="0786059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">驗＝證【聖】</note><app n="0786059"><lem wit="【大】">驗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">證</rdg></app>也。古<note n="0786060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">常＝尚【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0786060" resp="CBETA" type="mod">常＝尚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786060"><lem wit="【大】">常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">尚</rdg></app>如此況於
<lb n="0786c08" ed="T"/>今日，王熟思之無念<note n="0786061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婬妷＝婬泆【三】【宮】</note><note n="0786061" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婬妷＝婬泆【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0786061"><lem wit="【大】">婬妷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">婬泆</rdg></app>，無受侫言<note n="0786062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">證人入＝誤入人【三】【宮】，證入人【聖】</note><note n="0786062" resp="CBETA" type="mod">證人入＝誤入人【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，＝證入人【聖】</note><app n="0786062"><lem wit="【大】">證人
<lb n="0786c09" ed="T"/>入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">誤入人</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">證入人</rdg></app>罪，當受忠諫治以節度，當畏地獄酷治之
<lb n="0786c10" ed="T"/>痛，諸含血之<note n="0786063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蟲＝類【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0786063" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蟲＝類【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786063"><lem wit="【大】">蟲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">類</rdg></app>皆貪生活不當殺之。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0786c1015" rend="inline">佛說經
<lb n="0786c11" ed="T"/>竟，王意即解，願為弟子。即受五戒，頭面著地，
<lb n="0786c12" ed="T"/>為佛作<note n="0786064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">禮＋（而去）【聖】</note><app n="0786064"><lem wit="【大】">禮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">禮而去</rdg></app>。<note n="0786065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">光明皇后願文【聖】</note></p></cb:div>
